subtitleNullable: Historical daily prices of Cipla Ltd., an Indian MNC pharmaceutical company
descriptionNullable:
**Overview**
This dataset contains historical daily prices for Cipla Ltd. which is an Indian multi-national pharmaceutical company, headquartered at Mumbai, India. Cipla primarily develops medication to treat respiratory disease, cardiovascular disease, arthritis, diabetes, depression, and other medical conditions. It is the third largest drug producer in India.

This historic data has been retrieved from [Yahoo Finance](https://finance.yahoo.com/).
It contains prices starting from 1st January 2019 till present date. The data shall be expected to update on a quarterly basis. 

**Data Structure is as follows:**
**Each row contains the following features:
1) Date - specifies the trading date

2) Open - opening price

3) High - maximum price during the day

4) Low - minimum price during the day

5) Close - close price adjusted for splits

6) Adj Close - close price adjusted for both dividends and splits

6) Volume - the number of shares that changed hands during a given day**
